The paper deals with record linkage, which is a common problem in data management and analysis. The use of graphical models and probabilistic methods suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The problem of record linkage is also relevant to databases (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Finally, the use of classifiers and labeling techniques suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) sub-category.
